article.description: — Quincy Olivari recorded 30 points as Rice beat Texas State 83-71 on Sunday night.
article.headline: Olivari scores 30, Rice beats Texas State 83-71
article.linkText: Olivari scores 30, Rice beats Texas State 83-71
article.story: SAN MARCOS, Texas -- — Quincy Olivari recorded 30 points as Rice beat Texas State 83-71 on Sunday night. Olivari also had five rebounds for the Owls (6-2). Cameron Sheffield scored 13 points and grabbed six rebounds. Mekhi Mason added 13 points. Mason Harrell led the Bobcats (5-4) in scoring, finishing with 23 points. Drue Drinnon added 11 points for Texas State. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
